snippet.textDisplay:
Mai jb coaching jaat aur aata tha toh hamesha iss gaane ko suna krta tha.
Aaj jb kaafi samay ke baad sun rha toh aisa lg rha vo daur aa gya mai fir wahi raste pr chal rha jis raste se mai Jaya krta tha. 
Aaj kaafi dino baad ye gaana wapas sunkar dil ko sukoon aaya. Ab aisa ho rha ki kaas vo din hi rehta, iss gaane aur coaching tk ka vo road ka connection top notch ka ho gya hai. Aaj mai ye gaana toh sun rha pr uss raste aur uss jgh nhi khi aur.
Aaj jb wapas se sb yaad aa rha toh aisa lg rha kaash whi din rehte ya vo din wapas aa jata.
Feeling Nostalgic ❤
Missing that road from KARAUNDHI to BHU and that coaching too (MALVIYA ACADEMY ❤🥰)
